    <h2><strong>CONTINUOUS IMPROVEMENT</strong></h2>
    <p>In order for continuous improvement to be sustainable—not just happen in fits and starts—it must be made part of the culture of the organization; a matter of course every day for every team member. To make your organization’s culture truly one of continuous improvement, you need a deeper understanding of which ideal behaviors to cultivate within your workforce.</p>
