        <ul class="square">
            <li>Seek Perfection</li>
            <li id="align">Embrace Scientific Thinking</li>
            <li>Focus on Process</li>
            <li>Assure Quality at the Source</li>
            <li>Flow &amp; Pull Value</li>
        </ul>
    </p>
